<br>
If you have big issues with being hit go to a random very green camp and agro them all and just stand there and get smacked a bit, try to get off a few heals and see what it's like.  At higher lvls it's kinda expected that you know if you are agroed you wait to have the tank or chanter get it off you and not run around like a chicken with it's head cut off.  You should be able to take some hits as a cleric, not like tanking but if you get smacked a bit you should be okay with it.<br>
<br>
